    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842680/extras/b88a3afabe813912a8f08d9cc7abcdec.webp?t=1772230629\" width=615 height=45 /></span>作为一名宝藏猎人和冒险家，探索瓦坎布里亚岛广阔的风景，同时为当地岛民的自由而英勇奋斗。搜索各种生物群落、洞穴、废墟和城镇，同时解锁宝藏并解决谜题，以解放岛屿。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>参与激动人心的战斗</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842680/extras/05e32cd7ae5aab5b1570971c016d4d07.webp?t=1772230629\" width=615 height=5 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842680/extras/wi_action3.gif?t=1772230629\" /></span><br>拯救瓦坎布里亚岛，参与令人满意的战斗。你的敌人会猛烈扫射、招架并齐心协力试图阻止你的英勇努力。利用各种武器和战术让你的敌人屈服。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>定制你的冒险家</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842680/extras/05e32cd7ae5aab5b1570971c016d4d07.webp?t=1772230629\" width=615 height=5 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842680/extras/7adadf7cc3d8b26d1ffa12095625f4be.poster.avif?t=1772230629\" width=614 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842680/extras/7adadf7cc3d8b26d1ffa12095625f4be.webm?t=1772230629\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842680/extras/7adadf7cc3d8b26d1ffa12095625f4be.mp4?t=1772230629\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在整个瓦坎布里亚及其各种废墟和洞穴中解锁新的化妆品和盔甲。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索古代世界</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842680/extras/05e32cd7ae5aab5b1570971c016d4d07.webp?t=1772230629\" width=615 height=5 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842680/extras/00ebd228d7d879a142d4bc571a9ca7ff.poster.avif?t=1772230629\" width=614 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842680/extras/00ebd228d7d879a142d4bc571a9ca7ff.webm?t=1772230629\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842680/extras/00ebd228d7d879a142d4bc571a9ca7ff.mp4?t=1772230629\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>探索废墟、洞穴、寺庙和城镇等不同地点，发现瓦坎布里亚岛的秘密。瓦坎布里亚岛充满了秘密、宝藏和危险。 <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842680/extras/wishlist-today-24-green.png?t=1772230629\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>认识当地人</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842680/extras/05e32cd7ae5aab5b1570971c016d4d07.webp?t=1772230629\" width=615 height=5 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842680/extras/1d3cf301ea50cb0b628969d42610ad95.avif?t=1772230629\" width=614 height=180 /></span><br>当你迎接挑战以确保他们的自由时，与当地人成为朋友。瓦坎布里亚岛的人民是一群友善的人。当您在岛上冒险时，您有机会参与并帮助他们帮助您。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>购买和装饰您的家</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842680/extras/05e32cd7ae5aab5b1570971c016d4d07.webp?t=1772230629\" width=615 height=5 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842680/extras/66081d4c051c504979e5a30d6acf5a56.avif?t=1772230629\" width=614 height=180 /></span><br>购买众多游戏家园中的一处，并按照您的喜好装饰它们。购买材料或使用你在冒险中找到的物品来建造你自己的豪华居住区。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Wacambria Island</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842680/extras/05e32cd7ae5aab5b1570971c016d4d07.webp?t=1772230629\" width=615 height=5 /></span><br>Wacambria Island 是一款开放世界的动作角色扮演游戏，故事发生在一座由多种生物群系组成的岛屿上。扮演一名寻找宝藏的冒险家，却卷入了当地岛民与入侵军队之间的戏剧之中。由于该岛大部分由入侵军队控制，您需要与当地人合作才能夺回领土。这段旅程将带您穿越众多的生物群落、洞穴、废墟和城镇，同时发现古老力量和传奇英雄的秘密。由于当地人的处境不利，您将成为瓦坎布里亚岛自由的决定性因素。",
